Package algraph.windows

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddEdgeWindow
    Window used to add a new edge.
    EditEdgeWindow
    Window used to edit the weight of an existing edge.
    InfoWindow
    Window used to show info about the algorithm.
    NewWindow
    Window used to create a new graph(randomized).
    RemoveEdgeWindow
    Window used to remove an existing edge.
    RemoveNodeWindow
    Window used to remove an existing node.
    StartBFMWindow
    Window used to start the BFM algorithm.
